{
  "stem": "27340.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if I did, I suppose my parents [LAUGHS] would have tried very much to try and, uh, sort of, uh, prevent me from developing any, any further such views.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I think it's possibly inherent in all young boys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if you look at the young people today, they, they play with toy guns.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they play the hide and seek and coppers and, and, and thieves and red Indians and cowboys and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think this aggressiveness, perhaps, is inherent in all the male children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, uh, it was no different with us, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I said earlier, that Goring-- and he had a very good reason for this-- Goring, in fact, decreed that all those who had been with the Imperial German forces in the first World War should be released.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That also included my father and raised our hopes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, Buchenwald is a long distance away from Breslau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And because the inmates were all shaven and were in a very bedraggled sort of appearance, to say the very least, the Germans very cleverly transported them or let them go home by train only during the night so that the smallest possible number of German citizens would ever come across them.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I do remember that the train, the only train, that would, in fact, arrive in Breslau from Buchenwald-- I don't know that whether it was a direct train or whether one had to change somewhere-- would arrive in Breslau early in the morning at about 6:30.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was winter, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was plenty of snow on the ground.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
